{"post-87375": {"user": "Taingaard", "user_num": 3105, "timestamp": "1543707061000", "message": "Deep inside a long forgotten grove in the ancient forest of Thornwood where man, beast and nature become almost indistinguishable lies The First Tree Of Taingaard - the mythological Hindra.Whsipering to the forest and all nature in Taingaard as its roots are said to spread out covering the whole of the island the mytho-magical properties to Taingaard's nature origin from this tree and many in rural areas along with intelligent beasts treat it like a god. Those who have seen it tell of a grueling journey both physically and mentally to even get there and approaching the tree they were met with what sounded like a thousands whispering inquiries and those who didn't flee right there would be trialed in ways they would either not be able to put words to or refuse to tell about.\u00a0Only a few warriors have been deemed worthy by the tree to receive its blessings and only one have ever been granted the unique gift of being allowed to cut off a branch of its wood - an honor which is forever carved in history although the name of the champion was never known. One log of its wood is said to burn an eternity and the champion crafted a few weapons of legendary status that - despite not looking the part - was imbued with fantastic traits due to the origin of the wood used.\u00a0", "link_list": ["https://flic.kr/p/2cbVtxS", "https://flic.kr/p/2cbVtxS", "https://www.flickr.com/photos/137813549@N06/"], "image_list": ["https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4833/45412215564_5c56ae4de7_b.jpg"], "html": "<div style=\"text-align:center;\"><a href=\"https://flic.kr/p/2cbVtxS\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4833/45412215564_5c56ae4de7_b.jpg\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\"/></a><a href=\"https://flic.kr/p/2cbVtxS\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"></a><a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/137813549@N06/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"></a><br><br/